snippet.title: Disney's Stitch! Super Chef Trailer (iOS Puzzler)
snippet.description:
Download Link: https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/stitch!-super-chef/id582521172?mt=8

Ever since Reuben teased Angel for her (lack of) culinary skills, Stitch has made it his sole mission to become the ultimate sandwich chef. In doing so, he would ascend above Reuben's legendary sandwich making AND have the ability to give Angel a hands-on lesson! A win-win scenario.

    Match & swap with smooth controls
    Discover up to 49 tasty ingredients
    Challenge friends with your high scores

Available in Hong Kong, China, Taiwan & Macau in English/Traditional & Simplified Chinese
